---
title: Melt in the Middle Meatballs with Crispy Broccolini
description: Get ready for a surprise! Once you cut into these meatballs, gooey mozzarella oozes out from the center. The kids will go crazy! Crispy broccolini keeps this dinner balanced and wholesome.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/uk-melt-in-the-middle-meatballs-666b8b18.jpg
